the co-authors of "The
Third Reconstruction:
How a Moral Movement

00:18.100 --> 00:21.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Is Overcoming the Politics
of Division and Fear" about
their success in bridging those

00:22.200 --> 00:24.766 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
