00:24.766 --> 00:26.966 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT:
In recent weeks, Reverend
William Barber stepped
down from heading the

00:26.966 --> 00:31.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
