on what he calls a national
moral revival, updating the

00:34.066 --> 00:38.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Poor People's Campaign started
by the Reverend Martin Luther
King Jr. that linked the civil

00:38.666 --> 00:43.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
rights struggle for
African-Americans to demands for
equality for all poor people.

00:44.166 --> 00:46.666 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REV.

00:46.666 --> 00:48.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BARBER II, Co-Author,
"The Third Reconstruction:
How a Moral Movement Is
Overcoming the Politics

00:48.766 --> 00:50.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of Division and Fear": There was
this thing, if you will, called
the white Southern strategy.

00:50.466 --> 00:55.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
