make poor whites, who should
be allies with poor blacks,

01:14.666 --> 01:19.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
think that their problem,
their poverty is being caused
because black and brown people

01:19.633 --> 01:23.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
