taking something from them.

01:23.600 --> 01:27.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: So,
what led you to try and bridge
that gap, and what made you

01:27.933 --> 01:28.933 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
