01:28.933 --> 01:31.000 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REV.

01:31.000 --> 01:34.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BARBER II: Dr. King
said -- back in the '60s, he
said, the only transformative

01:34.166 --> 01:39.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
force that could really, fully
transform America would be for
poor whites and blacks and brown

01:40.300 --> 01:42.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
people and working
people to come together.

01:42.700 --> 01:47.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: Jonathan
Wilson-Hartgrove conversion
began when he first met Reverend

01:47.566 --> 01:49.600 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Barber.

01:49.600 --> 01:52.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
