77 percent Republican.

03:32.733 --> 03:37.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: Wary,
but undeterred, Reverend Barber
seized on the invitation of

03:37.266 --> 03:38.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
this rural white church.

03:38.500 --> 03:40.133 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REV.

03:40.133 --> 03:43.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BARBER II: I
went in and talked to
them for about an hour.

03:43.100 --> 03:48.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I said, listen, this
legislature just cut,
denied Medicaid expansion.

03:50.133 --> 03:54.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There are 1,000 people in this
county that would get health
care, and they can't be black,

03:55.766 --> 03:57.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
because there are no
black people are up here.

03:57.033 --> 03:58.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
They cut funding for
public education.

03:58.300 --> 04:02.066 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
You are losing teachers here.

04:02.066 --> 04:04.166 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And they have to be white.

04:04.166 --> 04:06.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Now, you voted for some of the
people because of what they
told you they stood on prayer

04:06.866 --> 04:11.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in school and abortion and
homosexuality, but let's look
at what they are doing, and

04:11.666 --> 04:13.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
how it is hurting you.

04:13.766 --> 04:17.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: So,
basically, what you did was to
talk to them about the things

04:19.233 --> 04:20.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
that they had in common.

04:20.833 --> 04:22.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And it registered.

04:22.566 --> 04:23.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It permeated their
consciousness.

04:23.833 --> 04:25.933 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REV.

04:25.933 --> 04:27.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BARBER II: You talk to
people honestly, you talk to
them about what it means to be

04:27.166 --> 04:30.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
a human being, and you
show them the hypocrisy.

04:30.733 --> 04:35.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You know, you show them how
they're being fooled, if you
will, that people are saying,

04:38.133 --> 04:40.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I care about your best
interests, but those
people are actually
putting in place policies

04:40.033 --> 04:42.100 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
that are hurting everybody.

04:42.100 --> 04:46.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: What
strategy did you use to reach
people who had been brought

04:46.800 --> 04:49.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
up like Jonathan?

04:49.033 --> 04:52.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What did you do to convince
them that this wasn't right?

04:52.400 --> 04:54.933 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REV.

04:54.933 --> 04:57.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BARBER II: I know
that many of my white
evangelical friends or
many African-Americans

04:57.533 --> 05:02.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
who were bought into
this kind of a public
engagement-type faith
really have been introduced

05:04.500 --> 05:08.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to -- and I say this sorrowfully
-- a form of heresy and a form
of theological malpractice.

05:10.566 --> 05:14.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
To try to suggest that Jesus
was just about a little prayer,
a little preaching and a

05:14.966 --> 05:19.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
little worship and a little
charity -- the very Jesus that
white evangelicals claim to

05:22.266 --> 05:25.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
lift up was a brown-skinned
Palestinian Jew whose
first sermon was
challenging the economic

05:26.433 --> 05:28.433 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
exploitation of the empire.

05:28.433 --> 05:32.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: Reverend
Barber and Wilson-Hartgrove
have been working together

05:32.066 --> 05:37.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in a multiracial movement known
as Moral Monday, weekly protests
held on the grounds of the

05:39.000 --> 05:43.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
North Carolina state capitol
in Raleigh aimed at helping
citizens understand their common

05:45.433 --> 05:49.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
interest around such issues
as health care, voting rights
and immigration, also how they

05:51.033 --> 05:55.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
are affected by these and
other governmental policies,
regardless of race or class.

05:55.766 --> 05:57.766 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REV.

05:57.766 --> 05:59.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BARBER II: When we went
into the first Moral Monday
in a diverse role as clergy,

05:59.933 --> 06:02.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
investment, first,
some people laughed.

06:02.033 --> 06:03.733 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They said we were a nuisance.

06:03.733 --> 06:07.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
But then they started
seeing more people come,
and they looked diverse.

06:07.733 --> 06:12.466 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They said, that's my
teacher getting arrested,
that's my doctor, that's
a black man and white

06:12.466 --> 06:13.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
man walking together.

06:13.666 --> 06:15.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
That's a Jew and a
rabbi and a Christian.

06:15.933 --> 06:18.033 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
What's going on?

06:18.033 --> 06:20.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, people began to think --
even though they didn't get
arrested, they would come.

06:20.633 --> 06:25.566 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT:
The Moral Monday movement
is the foundation for
Reverend Barber's latest

06:27.000 --> 06:29.500 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
project that he intends
to take to some 25 states.

06:29.500 --> 06:33.900 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JONATHAN WILSON-HARTGROVE:
What can be learned
from our experience is
that white people need

06:33.900 --> 06:36.733 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
to talk about race honestly.

06:36.733 --> 06:40.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We need to say, of
course we're racist.

06:40.900 --> 06:42.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
This is a country that's
built on white supremacy.

06:42.700 --> 06:45.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
You know, it's not like
it's a personal failing.

06:45.000 --> 06:46.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I inherited this.

06:46.966 --> 06:51.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Racism is about structures
that pass on what
we inherited, right?

06:53.600 --> 06:56.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Inequalities that we
inherited are written
into these structures.

06:56.433 --> 07:01.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And when we help white people
think about that, I think
we're making it possible to

07:02.833 --> 07:04.666 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
form alliances that we
haven't been able to form.

07:04.666 --> 07:06.133 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REV.

07:06.133 --> 07:07.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WILLIAM BARBER II: And black
people can't be afraid of that.

07:07.066 --> 07:09.133 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We have to look back in history.

07:09.133 --> 07:12.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
When black and white people
came together right after the
Civil War, we fundamentally

07:12.100 --> 07:14.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
changed this country.

07:14.166 --> 07:16.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
When black and white and brown
people and Jews and Christians
came together in the civil

07:16.266 --> 07:18.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
rights movement, it
was transformative.

07:18.333 --> 07:22.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: Are you
at all optimistic that the kinds
of things that you're doing

07:22.700 --> 07:27.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
are going to make a
difference in ending racism?

07:27.633 --> 07:32.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JONATHAN WILSON-HARTGROVE: I
think racism is the fundamental
challenge to the American

07:35.866 --> 07:37.966 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
project.

07:37.966 --> 07:41.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This is a country that was
built on the original sin of
race-based chattel slavery.

07:43.833 --> 07:47.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
It is how the, you know,
concentrated capital
in this country from
the very beginning has

07:47.533 --> 07:50.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
maintained power.

07:50.033 --> 07:54.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But I don't think that the
future of America is possible
without dealing with it.

07:54.800 --> 07:55.800 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REV.

07:55.800 --> 07:56.800 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BARBER II: I'm hopeful.

07:56.800 --> 07:58.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Optimism is a different thing.

07:58.766 --> 08:02.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I believe we have to be the
kind of what I call moral
dissenters, moral defibrillators

08:02.533 --> 08:04.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
who shock the nation.

08:04.166 --> 08:06.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But we also are seeing
something in the wind.

08:06.833 --> 08:09.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You have white people marching
with Black Lives Matter.

08:09.266 --> 08:12.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I had a friend of mine who's a
Sikh, and she put it like this.

08:12.400 --> 08:17.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Quickly, she said, a tomb
is dark and a womb is dark,
but there's a difference.

08:18.900 --> 08:20.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
A tomb is death, a
womb is possibility.

08:20.633 --> 08:22.566 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It's dark now.

08:22.566 --> 08:27.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But if we push and push together
and come together, I think
this is a birthing moment.

08:28.933 --> 08:30.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT:
